    "Figure 3 illustrates a common general chemistry problem where ChatGPT generates an incorrect pH value for a solution, resulting from an unrealistic molar concentration.",
    "In this case, the system calculates a pH of approximately -1.48, which is not physically meaningful for the concentration in question.",
    "Misconceptions and biases in AI responses arise when refined prompting elicits incorrect, incomplete, or biased information from language models.",
